tests.error:
Job failed and tunnel errors were found. This suggests interceptor tunnel was not created properly. Errors: ["Prompt learning job failed: Configuration incompatible: Remote task app cannot reach localhost interceptor.
  Task app URL: https://boring-monthly-voted-bureau.trycloudflare.com
  Interceptor URL: http://localhost:8000/api/interceptor/v1

Solutions:
  1. Deploy backend to Render/Modal (sets BACKEND_URL env var)
  2. Use local task app (localhost or 127.0.0.1)
  3. Set BACKEND_URL env var to your backend's public URL"]
